{"tid":1727881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請即加入行動：#NoMingJaiChallenge","createTime":"2019-11-16T15:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:35:56.000Z","uid":320074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac2ff6cb71e8404e640eabf337a45748d2bde37","tid":1727881,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"相信大家都睇過三個鐘之前既MingJai直播<br />\n可惜，Ming仔不但無發揮其KOL既重要功能<br />\n仲要喺度耍大牌，嘗試為自己既罪過辯護。<br />\n而且扮自己係淺黃，話自己兩邊都譴責。<br />\n所以，本人現正建立 #NoMingJaiChallenge<br />\n喺聲援發聲KOL如大J、屎萊姆等既同時<br />\n亦都希望呢個challenge可以作借鑒。<br />\n重申KOL喺極權之下既功能同效能。<br />\n抵抗極權，抵擋麻木。拒絕中立，還我良知。<br />\n<br />\n罪行：<br />\n1.耍大牌，自己喺直播明明話偷偷地捐錢。<br />\n但自己之後又話要捐助機構資料。自相矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n2.扮淺黃，話兩邊失控【示威者同POPO】都唔會原諒，但更加會譴責【部分警察】既行為<br />\n<br />\n3.Youtube神隱六個月，聲稱話YT只係成品集，但FB同IG無解釋點解唔更新YT。<br />\n<br />\n4.平行時空，香港打緊仗既同時自己喺FB IG度做港豬。自己喺反國教果陣明明主動發聲，宜家反而虛作無聲。<br />\n<br />\n【仲有一堆罪行待補充。】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xwq3mzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwq3mzv.jpg&h=a3a7a5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/16/231438_471b71e1675f4fdaf81349d91e439722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F16%2F231438_471b71e1675f4fdaf81349d91e439722.jpg&h=89e597fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往論政片段【但宜家又唔敢？】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OSK__qndQmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOSK__qndQmk&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=41ca8f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OSK__qndQmk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fZMMqmkGcFY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfZMMqmkGcFY&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=817c1507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fZMMqmkGcFY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=unrVsmPRA04&amp;feature=youtu.be\" da